# Shell scripts run under bash in WSL — CRLF breaks them at parse time
# (`set -euo pipefail\r` -> "invalid option name"). Force LF so a Windows checkout
# can't reintroduce CRLF. Surfaced by the 009 on-hardware sweep: build.sh/run.sh/
# embed_run.sh/tabular_run.sh/reseed_registry.sh/bootstrap.sh had CRLF and failed.
*.sh text eol=lf
